                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850223-88-off411 t17850223-88-cd412"></join>, twenty-seven yards of blue linsey, value 25 s. seven yards and three-quarters of kersey, value 7 s. and four yards of serge, value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17850223-88-victim924" type="victimName">
                  Birkhead 
                  Hitchcock
               <interp inst="t17850223-88-victim924" type="surname" value="Hitchcock"></interp>
